+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
|        Class        | Leading bits | Size of network number bit field | Size of rest bit field | Number of networks | Addresses per network |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
| Class A             | 0            | 8                                | 24                     | 128 (27)           | 16,777,216 (224)      |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
| Class B             | 10           | 16                               | 16                     | 16,384 (214)       | 65,536 (216)          |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
| Class C             | 110          | 24                               | 8                      | 2,097,152 (221)    | 256 (28)              |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
| Class D (multicast) | 1110         | not defined                      | not defined            | not defined        | not defined           |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
| Class E (reserved)  | 1111         | not defined                      | not defined            | not defined        | not defined           |
+---------------------+--------------+----------------------------------+------------------------+--------------------+-----------------------+
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  Total addresses in class | Start address |     End address    | Default subnet mask in dot-decimal notation | CIDR notation |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  2,147,483,648 (231)      | 0.0.0.0       | 127.255.255.255[a] | 255.0.0.0                                   | /8            |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  1,073,741,824 (230)      | 128.0.0.0     | 191.255.255.255    | 255.255.0.0                                 | /16           |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  536,870,912 (229)        | 192.0.0.0     | 223.255.255.255    | 255.255.255.0                               | /24           |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  268,435,456 (228)        | 224.0.0.0     | 239.255.255.255    | not defined                                 | /4[7]         |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
                  268,435,456 (228)        | 240.0.0.0     | 255.255.255.255[b] | not defined                                 | not defined   |
                 --------------------------+---------------+--------------------+---------------------------------------------+---------------+
n indicates a bit used for the network ID.
H indicates a bit used for the host ID.
X indicates a bit without a specified purpose.
Class A
  0.  0.  0.  0 = 00000000.00000000.00000000.00000000
127.255.255.255 = 01111111.11111111.11111111.11111111
                  0nnnnnnn.HHHHHHHH.HHHHHHHH.HHHHHHHH

Class B
128.  0.  0.  0 = 10000000.00000000.00000000.00000000
191.255.255.255 = 10111111.11111111.11111111.11111111
                  10nnnnnn.nnnnnnnn.HHHHHHHH.HHHHHHHH

Class C
192.  0.  0.  0 = 11000000.00000000.00000000.00000000
223.255.255.255 = 11011111.11111111.11111111.11111111
                  110nnnnn.nnnnnnnn.nnnnnnnn.HHHHHHHH

Class D
224.  0.  0.  0 = 11100000.00000000.00000000.00000000
239.255.255.255 = 11101111.11111111.11111111.11111111
                  1110XXXX.XXXXXXXX.XXXXXXXX.XXXXXXXX

Class E
240.  0.  0.  0 = 11110000.00000000.00000000.00000000
255.255.255.255 = 11111111.11111111.11111111.11111111
                  1111XXXX.XXXXXXXX.XXXXXXXX.XXXXXXXX
